data.description: Wanna be close to the lake, shopping and restaurants but far enough away to feel like you're in the country? Come see this immaculate home tucked away in private wooded lot. This split level home features 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms upstairs with 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom downstairs for a total living space of 2,081 sq ft. Outside you will find a beautifully designed deck perfect for entertaining guest or having a cup of coffee and watching the deer and other wildlife as they eat and play. This home is located .7 miles from Nix Bridge park and less than 5 miles to all the restaurants and shopping that Dawsonville has to offer
